{"tid":640171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下月結婚 準新人鴛鴦浴中毒身亡","createTime":"2018-04-24T05:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:46:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2dec88f6bcb9000ef4fc6a6afa34e2e63ab49fc4","tid":640171,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:48:18.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】台北市松山區三民路一棟民宅，21日晚發生一氧化碳中毒事件，意外造成2死2傷。<br />\n<br />\n21日晚8時許，37歲黃姓男子及其30歲許姓女友，雙雙倒臥浴室內，被發現時已經死亡，而住在樓上的一名70歲老翁與菲傭感身體不適，送醫治理。據了解死者為一對剛承租新屋半年的準新人，2人至今交往超過5年，去年拍完婚紗照，更準備在下月結婚，如今紅事變白事，雙方家屬更難過到一度昏厥。意外發生後消防及鑑識人員前往現場調查，發現屋主竟在半密閉式的空間內安裝戶外型熱水器，消防指「是從一個開放環境，變成密閉式或半密閉式。」<br />\n<br />\n根據2016年勸導單的紀錄，消防曾上門勸說當年的住戶要更換機型或遷移到適當場所，但卻遭當時住戶拒之門外。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i8MO.P5MDnikIj4BJcWtSg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-04-24/744df5f0-4767-11e8-b383-8f3214428b8c__2018042318182727047-side.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fi8MO.P5MDnikIj4BJcWtSg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-04-24%2F744df5f0-4767-11e8-b383-8f3214428b8c__2018042318182727047-side.jpg&h=fbc11f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A-%E6%BA%96%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E9%B4%9B%E9%B4%A6%E6%B5%B4%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1-102000107.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25A9%259A-%25E6%25BA%2596%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25B4%259B%25E9%25B4%25A6%25E6%25B5%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%25A1-102000107.html&d=vHuKfvF7bamx%2B%2BckcQho83Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=1cc6f484\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A-%E6%BA%96%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E9%B4%9B%E9%B4%A6%E6%B5%B4%E4%B8%AD%E6